div2.eg:
#VRML V2.0 utf8
# externproto definition of a single bar element EXTERNPROTO bar [ field SFInt32 x field SFInt32 y field SFInt32 z field SFString name ] "http://www.vrml.org/WorkingGroups/dbwork/barProto.wrl"
# inline containing the graph axes Inline { url "http://www.vrml.org/WorkingGroups/dbwork/barAxes.wrl" }
bar { x 10 y 9 z 7 name "North" }
bar { x 4 y 3 z 4 name "South" }
bar { x 6 y -1.5 z 2 name "West" }

item.p:
support for regular expressions for matching against any or
all of text nodes, attribute values, attribute names, element type
names;

a function string resolve(node-set) function
that treats the value of the argument as a relative URI and turns it
into an absolute URI using the base URI of the node;

additional attributes on xsl:sort to provide
further control over sorting, such as relative order of
scripts;
